<!-- ═══ ABOUT ═══ -->
<div class="section reveal has-bg" id="about">
  <div class="section__bg section__bg--strong section__bg--flip" data-align="right" aria-hidden="true">
    <canvas data-dynamics="logistic" data-direction="rtl" data-duration="2600" data-color="#5EC8FF"></canvas>
  </div>
  <p class="section__eyebrow">About</p>
  <h2 class="section__title">What I <em>do</em></h2>
  <div class="dyn-tag" aria-hidden="true"><span class="dyn-tag__kicker">Behind the text</span><span class="dyn-tag__name">Logistic map</span><span class="dyn-tag__sub">period-doubling bifurcation</span></div>
  <p class="section__desc">
    I work on resilience engineering, machine learning, and complex systems analysis at Embry-Riddle Aeronautical University. My research focuses on understanding why critical infrastructure fails under stress and developing methods to prevent it. I've secured over $86K in research funding, published 6+ peer-reviewed papers at venues like INCOSE, ASME, and AIAA, and I teach courses in signals and systems, optimization, and digital communications.
  </p>
  <p class="section__desc">
    Beyond academia, I consult with organizations and advise decision-makers in aerospace, energy, and public infrastructure, translating resilience research into strategies leaders can act on under uncertainty.
  </p>
  <a href="/about" class="section__more">Read the full story <span>&rarr;</span></a>
</div>

<div class="divider"><hr/></div>

<!-- ═══ RESEARCH ═══ -->
<div class="section reveal has-bg" id="research">
  <div class="section__bg section__bg--strong section__bg--flip" data-align="left" aria-hidden="true">
    <canvas data-dynamics="hopf" data-direction="ltr" data-duration="2400" data-color="#5EC8FF"></canvas>
  </div>
  <p class="section__eyebrow">Research</p>
  <h2 class="section__title">Recent <em>work</em></h2>
  <div class="dyn-tag" aria-hidden="true"><span class="dyn-tag__kicker">Behind the text</span><span class="dyn-tag__name">Hopf bifurcation</span><span class="dyn-tag__sub">birth of a limit cycle</span></div>
  <p class="section__desc">
    My research applies bifurcation theory, ecological network analysis, and reinforcement learning to problems in infrastructure resilience and autonomous systems.
  </p>
  <div class="cards stagger">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">Democratizing Resilience Analysis: Open-Source Tool Adaptation</div>
          <div class="card__org">INCOSE International Symposium 2026, Yokohama</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta"><span class="badge badge--pub">Accepted</span><br>Jun 2026</div>
      </div>
      <p class="card__desc">Adapting open-source tools for multi-stakeholder infrastructure resilience assessment.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">Evaluating Complex System Resilience Through BARD</div>
          <div class="card__org">Systems Engineering Journal</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta"><span class="badge badge--pub">Published</span><br>Apr 2026</div>
      </div>
      <p class="card__desc">A bifurcation-based diagnostic framework that quantifies system resilience across absorption, adaptation, and recovery phases.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">SAC Reinforcement Learning for Multi-Drone Search & Rescue</div>
          <div class="card__org">AIAA SciTech Forum 2026</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta"><span class="badge badge--pub">Published</span><br>Jan 2026</div>
      </div>
      <p class="card__desc">Soft actor-critic approach for autonomous multi-drone 3D terrain scanning and target detection.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card__top">
        <div>
          <div class="card__role">Bifurcation Analysis for System Resilience: Power Infrastructure</div>
          <div class="card__org">INCOSE International Symposium 2025</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__meta"><span class="badge badge--pub">Published</span><br>Jun 2025</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a href="/research" class="section__more">All publications & projects <span>&rarr;</span></a>
</div>

<div class="divider"><hr/></div>

<!-- ═══ GRANTS ═══ -->
<div class="section reveal has-bg" id="grants">
  <div class="section__bg section__bg--flip" data-align="left" aria-hidden="true">
